<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Şarj İstasyonları</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --mor: #7f00ff;
      --koyumor:rgb(66, 0, 132);
      --acikmor: #b388eb;
      --koyu: #1a002b;
      --beyaz: #ffffff;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0px;
      padding: 0px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--koyu), var(--mor));
      color: var(--beyaz);
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--acikmor), var(--beyaz));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #ccc;
      animation: fadeInDown 1.5s ease-out;
    }

    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--acikmor);
      color: var(--koyu);
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: bold;
      animation: fadeInUp 2s ease;
    }

    a.button:hover {
      background-color: var(--beyaz);
      color: var(--mor);
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(179, 136, 235, 0.7);
    }

    .Hepsi{
      width: 600px;
      height: 200px;
      margin: auto;
      margin-top: 250px;
    }

    .banner{
      width: 100%;
      height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--koyu), var(--koyumor));
      box-shadow: 3px 0px 30px #1a002b;
    }

    .banner a{
      float: right;
      margin-right: 20px;
      color: var(--acikmor);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 80px;
    }

    .banner a:hover{
      color: var(--beyaz)
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="banner">
    <a href="<%= charge_map_index_path %>" style="margin-right:40px">Ana Sayfa</a>
    <a href="<%= charge_map_info_path %>">Sitenin Amacı</a>
  </div>
  <div class="Hepsi">
    <h1>Project Şarj</h1>
    <p>Türkiye'deki tüm elektrikli araç şarj istasyonlarını tek haritada gör.</p>
    <a href="<%= charge_map_map_path %>" class="button">Haritaya Git</a>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
